snippet.title: CLeM (Mango Protocol) // The Mini Indie Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
A voice wakes you. It gives you a purpose. To achieve it you have a notebook with mysterious entries, and an entire house to explore. The moment has arrived to complete your mission. If you desire. If you are able.

Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1861440/CLeM/

The Mini Indie Showcase 2023: https://youtu.be/ANsVkLxB3e0 

Learn more: https://sixoneindie.com/showcase
